{"original": "BROWN: A question now on the economy."}
{"original": "CNN's JOHN KING: Campbell, Senators, good evening, first."}
{"original": "I want to bring the conversation back home. You know from your travels -- you don't need to look at the polls or anything else -- that the economy is by far now the dominant issue that voters want to hear about from the candidates."}
