{"original": "OBAMA: And that's an area where Senator Clinton and I may have a slight difference. But I'm happy to let her speak first and then can pick up on anything that's been left out."}
{"original": "KING: Let's give Senator Clinton that opportunity then."}
{"original": "As you have campaigned, Senator, on this issue and others, but specifically on this issue, you have said, I am ready on day one to take charge of the economy."}
