{"original": "In order to level the playing field for all students, we need to remove geographic barriers to college access and careers."}
{"original": "One solution is to create large supplements to the Pell Grant to help students without local college access."}
{"original": "An annual supplement of up to $5,000 for students from counties without a degree-granting college within their borders could help these students afford the high cost of relocating, according to our policy research."}
