{"original": "The President has made clear to his team that we should be reaching out to members of Congress from both parties to make the case for the rescue and engage with them and understand their concerns, Deese told reporters during a briefing on Friday."}
{"original": "It all underscores the message from the top -- the preferred route is a bipartisan one, and Biden still believes there is a pathway to at least 10 GOP votes for a relief proposal. What that proposal looks like, however, is obviously subject to negotiation, one official said. In other words, the $1.9 trillion proposal is an opening bid."}
