{"original": "Similarly, Biden will face a difficult challenge in balancing the need to address the climate crisis without worsening the jobs crisis facing the United States."}
{"original": "The Biden coalition is a very tenuous alliance between progressive environmentalists and organized labor, Josh Price, senior analyst at Height Capital Markets, said in an email."}
{"original": "The Biden plan calls for pouring trillions of dollars into clean energy, creating millions of union jobs while slashing carbon emissions."}
{"original": "However, Biden's legislative climate is in jeopardy because Democrats only have a slim majority in both houses of Congress. Moderate Democrats, including West Virginia Senator Joe Manchin, are unlikely to back sweeping climate action such as the Green New Deal or steps to strip the oil industry of tax breaks."}
