{"original": "They can identify themselves as IRS contractors."}
{"original": "The private collection firms' agents who work on taxpayer cases are not IRS employees. But they are working on the federal government's behalf and should indicate that. And they must be courteous and must respect taxpayer rights, according to the agency."}
