{"original": "ADP acknowledged this incident after it was revealed by cybersecurity reporter Brian Krebs and said it's working with a federal law enforcement task force to investigate what happened."}
{"original": "It's the latest example that shows how much personal information hackers have amassed on the black market -- and how it's being repurposed by identity thieves for all sorts of fraud."}
