{"original": "It will take several more months of easing before the economy and stock market begin to feel the benefit, said Chen Long, an analyst at research firm Gavekal."}
{"original": "Chinese stocks had a miserable 2018, suffering from the slowdown and the trade hostilities with the United States. And until stimulus measures start having a real effect, market momentum is going to deteriorate further, Long said."}
