{"original": "The campaign was launched by a group called SheSays, which aims to end gender-based discrimination."}
{"original": "The right for women to have access to menstrual hygiene and sanitation is absolute, said Trisha Shetty, the founder of SheSays. Women should not be discriminated against on the grounds of a natural bodily function."}
